column5: Has anyone found any fishing show coupons (2 for 1, 1/2 price, etc.) anywhere? Thanks. Jim
Hi, I've seen then in a few tackle shops so I assume most would have them if they're not already gone..............i believe it's $2 off   cheers
If you go to ANY of the  LeBARON STORE LOCATIONS  , they're giving away $2 OFF coupons to their customers... You can even grab however many you need!
